{"tid":1334701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【任達華遇襲】傳肝頂部見小氣泡　醫生稱兩大可能　或刺穿腸胃","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T10:32:11.000Z","uid":113626,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3bcb164ff1cc4dd4d214e8e2dd161f1cf807edd9","tid":1334701,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/354238/任達華遇襲-傳肝頂部見小氣泡-醫生稱兩大可能-或刺穿腸胃\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F354238%2F%E4%BB%BB%E9%81%94%E8%8F%AF%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E5%82%B3%E8%82%9D%E9%A0%82%E9%83%A8%E8%A6%8B%E5%B0%8F%E6%B0%A3%E6%B3%A1-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD-%E6%88%96%E5%88%BA%E7%A9%BF%E8%85%B8%E8%83%83&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvblGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=209c3db7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/354238/任達華遇襲-傳肝頂部見小氣泡-醫生稱兩大可能-或刺穿腸胃</a><br />\n<br />\n藝人任達華今日（20日）在中山出席商業活動途中，一名身穿灰色上衣的男子走上舞台，手持利器刺向任達華的腹部，任達華受傷送院。網上流傳任達華的診斷報告，部份內容提到他的左側腹直肌局部見小氣泡，前方脂肪密度增高，肝頂部見小氣泡。香港外科專科醫生夏威根據網上流傳的報告內容推測，出現氣泡有兩個可能性，包括空氣跟隨利器進入身體，以及體內有空氣的器官被刺穿。"},{"pid":"b073135332967f095673622a6b594b632569604e","tid":1334701,"uid":46966,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D大陸人真係唔知咩叫私隱"},{"pid":"ac3744964dfbc22ed1b0ce66f7cff3d752e16c29","tid":1334701,"uid":30163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:06:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"dde1f336253e7a527c78f91b959b4a8a331aaab4","tid":1334701,"uid":19676,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:08:25